org.eclipse.scada.configuration.globalization

Interface Global

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GlobalImpl

    public interface Global
    A representation of the model object 'Global'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Global
    • Default Logon Credentials
    • Locals
    • Event Pool Imports
    • Monitor Pool Imports
    • Local Pull
    • Filters

    See Also:
    GlobalizePackage.getGlobal()
